Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.22,0:00:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I just explained, the purpose of this operation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is to collect all physical data, including her ability to transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merely collecting more data on her seems like a halfway measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fight without knowing your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our past failures are a case in point.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, I will join this operation, to observe first-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, that's too risky!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might come into contact with the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to observe her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, executive commanders who always remain in safe places
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,garner no respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you intend to collect the data yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be accompanied by someone who has already been studying the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the target's research is proceeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can give you a report very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can collect data first-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:50.63,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,The constellations that decorate the summer night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:56.34,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,The diamonds start to twinkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:02.26,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting go into the time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:08.64,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to warm the body, tired from swimming
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:20.95,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended not to notice the smile that hides the loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:28.16,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's an endless dream (Keep on going)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:33.25,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight and shine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:40.09,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in your true self (It's up to you)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:45.26,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:53.52,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Look only at the irreplaceable future
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:05.03,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,322)}Delmo Operation: White Silver
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are a private enterprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,currently working for another government as a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are here because we've encountered a situation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we can't handle by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super activation materials,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,encased in variably structured ceramics and magnetically sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We call it Matoryoshika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the great land submergence, our institution sank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since that time, the Matoryoshika has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The map we had before was completely useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've investigated several times, but our operators couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we would like to get the famous special A-rank salvager,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Aika Sumeragi's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll soon arrive at the remains of our Air Force base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all white.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Base preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Landing altitude determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Etsuko Mina, I'm the head of this base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aika Sumeragi. Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were awaiting your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President and Ms. Vice President, thank you for bringing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything happen while I was gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, everything is proceeding smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very extensive base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand why you wanted an aerial investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the probe plane I want you to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We remodeled a military spy plane
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and built in some high performance probe equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's big.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a kid, Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she is very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rie Petriakov.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aika Sumeragi, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've heard bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're operating a very powerful plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its maximum speed is Mach 3.2.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's built-in high performance probe equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can probe a wide range of areas in a short amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing, Miss. Aika,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before you operate this plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we want you to take a physical and functional examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need adaptability to operate this plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very simple exam. It won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Examination? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rie, I'll let you take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody else, please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is not very flexible, Miss. Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go. See, 14 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right. Can we move on to the next test?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left hand on number 35.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right foot on number 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Do these poses have something to do with flying a plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that girl is doing weird things to Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to peep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quietly, quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't peep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do I have to do more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl Rie must be doing weird things to Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she won't let me in. Something's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why don't you work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you slow it down a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next! 9 Gs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next! 11 Gs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take off her clothes and place her on the operating table.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we will start the real examination, Miss Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will explore your secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you your accommodations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, is Miss Sumeragi's examination done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it will take a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey! What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Well? Answer me! Why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was all a Delmo trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Michikusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! We're collecting satisfactory data from the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, you can leave all the remaining work to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to go back to headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can an Executive Commander leave in the middle of the operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did you wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I went a little too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, are you trying to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, can you tell us more about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear more too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't tell you any interesting stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, drink more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've already had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. Please have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mr. Aida?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to seem rude,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems like I've met all of you once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you sing a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have karaoke in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why not? Just one song.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sing as many songs as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't you join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this switch on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That multi-axis trainer wore me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still feeling chest pains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were very sexy when you were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is really a weird girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Aika, what do you want to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry, I don't have any alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion! What's Michikusa doing here too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! You're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, I'm all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika! This place isn't a private corporate facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Delmo base!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, these Delmos?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl, Rie, must be a Delmo too! I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to leave here right now, Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think we have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally found out the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That costume! Rie, you're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Miss Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Delmo, Rie! That's my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found out the truth very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore our story,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about asking your help to investigate the Matoryoshika,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and other things, including this examination to operate the plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and of course, everything else was all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were so easily fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so innocent and cute for an older woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a lie, then there must be a real purpose behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo! That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing we really wanted to get was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-daaa! The data on Miss Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, I got a full load of your data.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything from head to toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the last thing I have to take is your fighting data.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great! Watching this live is much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika, you were great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika! Your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, what's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you disturbing me when I'm having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you decided to do as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if people laugh at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll live my life only one way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've something interesting to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I checked every part of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michikusa, you don't have to see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check inside her body next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside her body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anesthesia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you see, I've gotten all the data from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to study your strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and use it to make our "Delmogeny" even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already studied the way you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I have to find my data.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika! There's a sign saying "Data Room"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She does make a fast getaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm really mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion! Go find the President and prepare to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About forty steps...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering Rie's physique, she's about forty meters ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:19:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to call them when we find the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she doesn't come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The target is approaching. We will hold her off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh! I've got a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michikusa, what the hell are you wearing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible danger! Terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You reek of liquor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you drink at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not so simple to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an emergency! The base is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. The Delmos tricked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me to prepare to escape and wait for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Streak! Come in! Blue Streak! Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Streak! Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Red Top! Blue Streak! Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody is responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rie, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the data. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, Rie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take care of it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were all Delmos after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give the data back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hargen is gone now. Why must you continue this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mr. Hargen is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And perhaps we don't need to exist anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since the Delmos were created to serve Mr. Hargen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still have pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika Sumeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will defeat you and show our loyalty to Mr. Hargen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is our will!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:24:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cramped...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion, it's a little tight, but be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.54,0:24:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let you escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.76,0:24:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Max power!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.52,0:24:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rie!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.78,0:24:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Rie!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.73,0:25:48.06,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,So dance with me tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.06,0:25:52.44,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not above being cool for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.44,0:25:56.57,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, tell me what you want, what you want
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.57,0:26:00.49,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,In the hardest time, you still look so good to me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.49,0:26:04.91,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can ease your mind, ease your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.91,0:26:08.79,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have your fears just like every man
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.79,0:26:12.63,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Cannot be sure of yourself all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.25,0:26:17.59,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Just close your eyes, I'll turn the music on
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.59,0:26:21.60,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're gonna do what you got to do
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.14,0:26:29.77,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,So dance with me tonight, 'cause I make you feel all right
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.48,0:26:33.65,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Who fell in love at sight? I don't want to make a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.61,0:26:37.82,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Just dance with me tonight, if you wanna hold me tight
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.82,0:26:40.95,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say maybe, come to me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.74,0:26:46.12,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,So dance with me tonight, 'cause I make you feel all right
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.87,0:26:50.46,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Who fell in love at sight? I don't want to make a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.00,0:26:54.59,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Just dance with me tonight, if you wanna hold me tight
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.59,0:26:57.47,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say maybe, come to me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.06,0:27:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Delmo's fierce attack
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.69,0:27:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mercilessly destroys the K2 Corporation and Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.57,0:27:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika! Aika! Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.53,0:27:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.62,0:27:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, Papa, don't you feel anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.99,0:27:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost Aika, and our company.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.25,0:27:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.58,0:27:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive them! I'll never forgive them!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.25,0:27:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get revenge for Aika! Let's go, Michikusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.05,0:27:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a battle to avenge Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.09,0:27:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion, wait! Don't be a fool! Don't be so hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.55,0:27:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion breaks into the Delmo base with Gusto and Meipia.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.14,0:27:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika, next trial!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.35,0:28:04.15,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,330)}Decisive Break-in! Delmo Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.65,0:27:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decisive Break-in! Delmo Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.73,0:27:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A blue flower whirls in jet-black darkness.
